cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper presents a novel architecture that merges sequence and computer vision architectures for cross-domain sequence modeling. This suggests that the paper could belong to multiple sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, given the focus on deep learning architectures and achieving state-of-the-art results on time series data sets, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories.
